  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provide Education to 12 Orphan Children in India</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IDRF supports free residential care for destitute children in a friendly and caring environment which makes them feel at home. The orphanage known as &apos;Brindavan&apos; in Chennai, Tamil Nadu, provides care for 12 abandoned and orphan children who are vulnerable to exploitation by criminals and anti-social elements. The objective of this program is to provide good schooling &amp; extra-curricular activities to these children so as to help them stand on their own feet as adults and become good citizens.</narrative>
  </description>
